        ]

### Add a New User [POST]

One can easily add his information in listvusing the following - 
1. Name    
2. ID

For adding the new User the POST method is implemented.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "Name": "Shaon",
            "ID": "120"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /campus/user/4

    + Body

            {
                "id": "4",
                "Name": "Shaon",
                "ID": "120"
            }

